ActIndian Act
SubjectAddition to the Rainy River First Nations No. 4, Ontario
PrecisOrder setting apart 1,459.148 hectares (3,605.632 acres) of land including mines and minerals for the use and benefit of the Rainy River First Nations as an addition to RAINY RIVER FIRST NATIONS NO. 4, located in the District of Rainy River and is approximately 42 kilometres from Fort Frances, in Ontario.
